# PyBrowser Theme API

## Creating a Theme

You can create custom themes for PyBrowser by writing a CSS file that styles the browser's UI.

### Example CSS File

```css
/* Filename: my_custom_theme.css */

QWidget {
    background-color: #282c34;
    color: #abb2bf;
}

QLineEdit {
    background-color: #1c1f26;
    color: #ffffff;
}

QPushButton {
    background-color: #61afef;
    color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
}

QPushButton:hover {
    background-color: #528bff;
}

/* Add more custom styles here */
